{"type": "article", "id": 30704, "title": "有了这种模块化家具，你可以带着厨房搬家｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31181, "name": "STUDIO BANANA THiNGS"}, {"id": 31182, "name": "Kim Kim Lab"}, {"id": 31183, "name": "HRIBARCAIN"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 31184, "name": "Dikla Libresco"}, {"id": 31185, "name": "Natalia Geci"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 142, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160807230624pDKWISAJC4yYXQ8v.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Kangaroo Light by STUDIO BANANA THiNGS</h3><p>你见过可以用“片”作量词的灯吗？<a href=\"http://studiobananathings.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">STUDIO BANANA THiNGS</a> 推出的 Kangaroo Light 就是这么一“片”会发光的“毯子”。它是一款仅重 149 克、12 毫米厚的便携式灯具，正六边形的硅胶灯罩可以根据需要折叠成各种形状，兼具实用性与装饰性。除了用作夜灯或者气氛灯之外，你还可以把它放在包内随身携带，这样就不用担心在一片漆黑的情况下在包里手忙脚乱地翻找物品了。这是它的<a href=\"http://studiobananathings.com/products/kangaroo-light\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格为 75.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230930TMKLf35DFhZ7gxdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230930d2JRtS3BOELf4XN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230930pGaQVIugJkZXYhEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230930zthuPWJSTafs8pOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230930gu91jbKiS0dHfPeq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608072309304nQBxOANLsPpeVmy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Do you know the warm ice cream? by Kim Kim Lab</h3><p>夏天中甜蜜的烦恼之一或许就是融化得太快的冰激凌了。来自韩国的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kimkimlab/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kim Kim Lab</a> 就突发奇想，为那些变得温暖的冰激凌设计了一系列可爱的表情，巧妙地将这些造型与蜡烛结合在一起，并将这个系列命名为 Do you know the warm ice cream。看着这些“萌化”的冰激凌蜡烛，还真的有些舍不得点燃。目前这个设计还处于原型阶段，尚未开始销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230856UfTN9bvJtmYZHM4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230856pGTOz1Sm6dfR8bKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608072308566gd0fDHjt8xSCRyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230856Ufte92Pu3hz5QrKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230856VQG4l5LvMCnBfdyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230857fYK804FoBQuOCmHZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.493888\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Musiclips Lab by Dikla Libresco</h3><p>要说到古灵精怪的脑洞，<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 旗下的产品总是能够让人在日常生活中收获一份惊喜。它最新推出的多功能夹子 Musiclips 是以色列设计师 Dikala Libresco 的作品，一大一小分别为两种音符的造型。有了它，你可以直接以晾衣绳为谱，让晾衣服变得更加有趣。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/musiclips-multi-purpose-pegs\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 10 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230836xiRaqU5bKMncSP1H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230836y9PjZqXWzCd1AJa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230835QhyxJotBjzTcwN7n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230836SKWgTBv0DCf2lb8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MAGNO by HRIBARCAIN</h3><p>由设计团队 <a href=\"http://hribarcain.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HRIBARCAIN</a> 推出的 MAGNO 是一支富有未来感的自动铅笔，利用磁性来精准地调整铅芯，免去了过去需要一点点通过按钮来调整的麻烦。MAGNO 的铅芯由一块钕磁固定，转动笔套尾部的开关将笔芯解锁后，笔芯就会根据金属圆环的位置移动。MAGNO 的笔套由航空级别的铝材料制成，极简的设计看起来干净利落，不仔细看或许还会错认为钢笔。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/238708282/magno-the-worlds-first-magnetically-controlled-pen\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 25 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230737AwWuoUaqcCnx18sh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671949\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608072307376e42NYSAbHuGnUpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608072307381f4oc7gOjbHlhLmC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230739pQNC69yesUk0zTr8.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ember Mug by Eric Fields &amp; Martin Gschwandtl</h3><p>在饮料的世界里，再细小的温度差都会带来口感上的变化。为了让人喝到温度刚刚好的饮料，Eric Fields 和 Martin Gschwandtl 共同研发了一款名为 <a href=\"https://embertech.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ember Mug</a> 的智能保温杯，可以让饮料长时间保持在用户设定的温度下。调整温度时只需要旋转保温杯底部即可，除此之外也可以通过配套的应用进行预设，还能在华氏/摄氏两种温标间进行切换。这是它的<a href=\"https://store.embertech.com/cart/11856634307:1\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230709dSl25r1keYqvbFoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230709XiUBvHfndp3KP58N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230710IXjlpYOo7HQxUuGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230710y0Vg1G4sq6eINbXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230709Jftm4dryC57SwWQc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230710oS0um4DKrUxpF5wG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LYNKO by Natalia Geci</h3><p>阿根廷建筑师及设计师 <a href=\"http://www.nataliageci.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Natalia Geci</a> 希望可以为那些因为各处奔波而居无定所、每次搬家都会苦恼家具去处的人们创造一种更符合他们“这种游牧型”生活方式的家具。这个名为 LYNKO 的模块型家具系列包含架子、托盘、钩子等组件，能够同可折叠的金属框架、木制铰链以及收纳袋自由组合在一起，打造出小型的办公区、梳妆台，甚至是一间厨房。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230642tQ8xzAYnVmCp4IjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230641NRhHw4rIE5TXqmGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.151667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230642kA1jdZJ8DHS4TpnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230642rSZLEUPuR1AB8JqW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608072306427wPn39aUIxitmsL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.355000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230642ufpxqjLk4mCrEzMJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}